DESIGN EXPLORATION - STATUS: UGLY / UNCERTAIN

Auto-threading looked elegant but has problems:
1. Parser needs to handle event-name without () - violates "dumb parser"
2. Complex branch destructuring - which fields thread? All? Matching names?
3. Optional params get auto-filled when you wanted to omit them
4. Implicit magic vs "explicit for AI" principle

Keeping as design artifact. May revisit, may abandon.
Explicit threading is verbose but honest.
